{
  "name": "Hide",
  "type": "basicAction",
  "img": "icons/svg/cowled.svg",
  "system": {
    "description": "<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; scrollbar-width: thin; scrollbar-color: var(--color-scrollbar) var(--color-scrollbar-track); margin: 0.5em 0px; color: rgb(25, 24, 19); font-family: 'Trebuchet MS', 'Lucida Sans Unicode', 'Lucida Grande', 'Lucida Sans', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: start\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Trebuchet MS', 'Lucida Sans Unicode', 'Lucida Grande', 'Lucida Sans', Arial, sans-serif\">You can spend<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; scrollbar-width: thin; scrollbar-color: var(--color-scrollbar) var(--color-scrollbar-track);\"> 1 AP</strong> to attempt to Hide from 1 or more creatures that can’t see you (<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; scrollbar-width: thin; scrollbar-color: var(--color-scrollbar) var(--color-scrollbar-track);\">Unseen</strong>).</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; scrollbar-width: thin; scrollbar-color: var(--color-scrollbar) var(--color-scrollbar-track); margin: 0.5em 0px; color: rgb(25, 24, 19); font-family: 'Trebuchet MS', 'Lucida Sans Unicode', 'Lucida Grande', 'Lucida Sans', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: start\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Trebuchet MS', 'Lucida Sans Unicode', 'Lucida Grande', 'Lucida Sans', Arial, sans-serif\">Make a Stealth Check against the opposing creature’(s)<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; scrollbar-width: thin; scrollbar-color: var(--color-scrollbar) var(--color-scrollbar-track);\"> Passive Awareness</strong>.</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; scrollbar-width: thin; scrollbar-color: var(--color-scrollbar) var(--color-scrollbar-track); margin: 0.5em 0px; color: rgb(25, 24, 19); font-family: 'Trebuchet MS', 'Lucida Sans Unicode', 'Lucida Grande', 'Lucida Sans', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: start\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Trebuchet MS', 'Lucida Sans Unicode', 'Lucida Grande', 'Lucida Sans', Arial, sans-serif\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; scrollbar-width: thin; scrollbar-color: var(--color-scrollbar) var(--color-scrollbar-track);\">Success: </strong>You become <strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; scrollbar-width: thin; scrollbar-color: var(--color-scrollbar) var(--color-scrollbar-track);\">Hidden </strong>from creatures whose <strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; scrollbar-width: thin; scrollbar-color: var(--color-scrollbar) var(--color-scrollbar-track);\">Passive Awareness </strong>you beat (making you <strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; scrollbar-width: thin; scrollbar-color: var(--color-scrollbar) var(--color-scrollbar-track);\">Unseen </strong>and <strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; scrollbar-width: thin; scrollbar-color: var(--color-scrollbar) var(--color-scrollbar-track);\">Unheard </strong>by them).</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; scrollbar-width: thin; scrollbar-color: var(--color-scrollbar) var(--color-scrollbar-track); margin: 0.5em 0px; color: rgb(25, 24, 19); font-family: 'Trebuchet MS', 'Lucida Sans Unicode', 'Lucida Grande', 'Lucida Sans', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: start\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Trebuchet MS', 'Lucida Sans Unicode', 'Lucida Grande', 'Lucida Sans', Arial, sans-serif\">You remain <strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; scrollbar-width: thin; scrollbar-color: var(--color-scrollbar) var(--color-scrollbar-track);\">Hidden </strong>until you make a noise louder than a whisper, make an Attack, cast a Spell with a Verbal Component, or a creature takes the Search Action and successfully locates you.</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; scrollbar-width: thin; scrollbar-color: var(--color-scrollbar) var(--color-scrollbar-track); margin: 0.5em 0px; color: rgb(25, 24, 19); font-family: 'Trebuchet MS', 'Lucida Sans Unicode', 'Lucida Grande', 'Lucida Sans', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: start\"></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; scrollbar-width: thin; scrollbar-color: var(--color-scrollbar) var(--color-scrollbar-track); margin: 0.5em 0px; color: rgb(25, 24, 19); font-family: 'Trebuchet MS', 'Lucida Sans Unicode', 'Lucida Grande', 'Lucida Sans', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: start\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Trebuchet MS', 'Lucida Sans Unicode', 'Lucida Grande', 'Lucida Sans', Arial, sans-serif\"><em>See @UUID[Compendium.dc20rpg.rules.JournalEntry.37625d2c20f4d3ba.JournalEntryPage.abbf2175525f85e0]{Hidden Creatures} (@UUID[Compendium.dc20rpg.rules.JournalEntry.37625d2c20f4d3ba.JournalEntryPage.2a0a764530aca6af]{Unseen}, @UUID[Compendium.dc20rpg.rules.JournalEntry.37625d2c20f4d3ba.JournalEntryPage.635a365faf844c57]{Unheard}, @UUID[Compendium.dc20rpg.rules.JournalEntry.37625d2c20f4d3ba.JournalEntryPage.699fbe45d7fd755f]{Hidden}) for more on hiding.</em></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 'Trebuchet MS', 'Lucida Sans Unicode', 'Lucida Grande', 'Lucida Sans', Arial, sans-serif\"><em>When you take the Hide Action and beat an enemy’s Passive Awareness, you only become Hidden from that creature because it can’t see or hear you (you’re both Unseen and Unheard). However, if your Stealth Check beats one enemy’s Awareness Score but not another’s, then you’re Hidden from the first enemy, but you’re not Hidden from the second enemy.</em></span></p>",
